_:N94b506832918422f80e4ed9544466c16 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Nesil Caliskan was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State in the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government on 12 May 2026.</p>\n\n<p>She was previously Comptroller of HM Household (Government Whip) from 7 September 2025 to 12 May 2026. She was elected as the MP for Barking in July 2024.</p>\n" .
